commit_message: Upgraded older bwa to bwa-mem. No longer supporting older Illumina encoding.
Added compulsory queue field to pipeline_stages_config; updated default modules excepting GATK to work with merri - temporary measure.
Set default walltimes to minimal values rather than large-data values; removed obsolete batch queue.
Updated python version in VLSCI-cluster specific docs
Added a small amount of test data for the WGS version of the pipeline.
Added error message if no input files found.
Fixed initial symlinks to correctly handle relative paths.
Added acknowledgements to docstring; improved text.
Added links and code syntax to README.
First commit for releaseable version of basic variant-calling and annotation pipeline.
